sub_title: Operations Coordinator and Policy Officer at Musicians Without Borders
summary:
I am an enthusiastic, honest and reliable person. In addition, I have proven capacities to work in multicultural teams and I speak four languages. Characteristics that I highly value in myself are empathy and the capacity to collaborate with people of all ages, culture and experience. 
I am particularly interested in displacement of populations, climate change and diversity, equity and inclusion issues.
